Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------AVAN-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.14,0:00:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多纳托斯 博斯威尔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.78,0:00:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱茵迈尔 强尼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.50,0:00:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯蓝 托尼 维拉德
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.39,0:00:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利普利 梅希蒂德 梅悠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.68,0:00:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 让我一用吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------PRE------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.29,0:00:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摸摸他们的头有什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.46,0:00:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是自己儿子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.48,0:00:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这身怪物的特性传染了就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.95,0:00:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 这样就会传染的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:00:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是早就成怪物了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.90,0:01:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从身体变成这样以后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.94,0:01:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我见过太多死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.38,0:01:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只要将其看作广大世界洪流中的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.24,0:01:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就不会太难过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.16,0:01:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次碰到美丽或不可思议的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.97,0:01:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就会觉得接受这身体活下去也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.21,0:01:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都是这样想的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.26,0:01:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特丽莎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.62,0:01:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在与你邂逅并有了孩子之前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.13,0:01:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会变老
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.48,0:01:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我的孩子们却在一天天成长
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.88,0:01:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我突然觉得很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.60,0:01:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得自己真的是个怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.96,0:01:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公 你过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.44,0:01:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.65,0:01:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.08,0:01:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摄影师？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.76,0:02:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 领带系好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.30,0:02:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一家人还没拍过合照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.80,0:02:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么突然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.15,0:02:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 抱着爱德
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.27,0:02:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.76,0:02:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.17,0:02:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真伤脑筋…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.95,0:02:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 请看这边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.47,0:02:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要动哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.24,0:02:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会变成像怪物一样皱巴巴的老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.33,0:02:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论变成什么样子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.89,0:02:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是希望能全家一起笑着拍照
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.26,0:02:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 希望你永远做我们的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.25,0:02:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要刻意保持距离 主动疏远我们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.04,0:02:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也别再说「怪物」这种话 伤害自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 要拍了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.80,0:03:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公 笑一个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本打算接受这身体 继续活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.55,0:03:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想跟特丽莎和孩子们一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.22,0:03:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起变老 死去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.92,0:03:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.59,0:03:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.36,0:03:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.27,0:04:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修理秋千
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.37,0:04:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你做这种不习惯的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.74,0:04:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从来没为他们做过什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.74,0:04:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点事总该做了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特丽莎 我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.54,0:04:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.01,0:04:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.89,0:04:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跟孩子们提关于我身体的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.71,0:04:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用叫醒他们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.56,0:04:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到他们的脸 我会…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.94,0:04:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真傻 哭一下又有什么打紧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…哎呀 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.89,0:04:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起这么早
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.29,0:04:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔说要尿尿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.21,0:04:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 你帮忙照顾阿尔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.82,0:04:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 爱德
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.94,0:05:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTA-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.61,0:07:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.81,0:07:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 还是接不通
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.85,0:07:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真麻烦 联系不到上面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.80,0:07:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 要继续前进吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.97,0:07:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了放挖出来的土石 应该有出口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.72,0:07:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再往前走走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史密斯回去报告
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.39,0:07:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.09,0:07:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.62,0:07:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.02,0:08:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对完全不死的军团有兴趣么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.65,0:08:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上钩了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.57,0:08:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长生不老 你也有兴趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.33,0:08:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想一刀砍死他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.75,0:08:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 您的话太突然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.96,0:08:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一时不知该怎么回答
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.43,0:08:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有兴趣还是没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.48,0:08:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答案就是二选一嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.67,0:08:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不死梦想实现的日子来临之时
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.69,0:08:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除我以外
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.20,0:08:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的士兵们也能享受这恩惠吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那一天真的来临的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.81,0:08:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说这一点没有保证啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是答应他们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.34,0:09:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会被迫协助在我布里格斯引发事件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.71,0:09:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不答应的话就要换个代用的棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大概要左迁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 怎么回答才能万全呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.90,0:09:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报告 地下隧道先遣队…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地下隧道怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.84,0:09:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无妨 说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.43,0:09:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.33,0:09:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先遣队情况异常
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.81,0:09:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 这就去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.62,0:09:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 移动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.49,0:09:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.18,0:09:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得用上这玩意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:09:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 巴卡尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.13,0:10:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 正将艾尔利克兄弟从东牢移送至西牢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.70,0:10:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.49,0:10:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔尔夫·J·金布利氏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.64,0:10:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷文中将的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.86,0:10:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金布利？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.37,0:10:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红莲之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.87,0:10:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾尔利克兄弟不就是钢之炼金术师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.75,0:10:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 真是名副其实
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是这位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这段子真是久违了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.07,0:10:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教 钢之炼金术师先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.64,0:10:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.48,0:10:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.00,0:10:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行隧道探查的部队失去联系了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.65,0:10:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其后只有史密斯的马…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着应该是他的手臂回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.10,0:10:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有手臂…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.93,0:10:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行踪不明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.53,0:10:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所乘的马也太过激动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.99,0:10:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法使用了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:11:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亨舍尔 出动救援部队
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.67,0:11:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行 阿姆斯特朗少将
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.53,0:11:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个洞穴太危险
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.65,0:11:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个不死身的生物兵器到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.98,0:11:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它放回原处封住入口 少将
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.99,0:11:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.37,0:11:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在跟少将说话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.88,0:11:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这里的规矩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服从强者 服从力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.73,0:11:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姆斯特朗少将
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.03,0:11:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是中央市的雷文
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.29,0:11:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情总统阁下都告诉我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.32,0:11:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.37,0:11:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你们没说多余的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.23,0:11:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是约定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你不太服气
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.98,0:11:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人掌握了人质
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.70,0:11:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有不满才奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.26,0:11:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 啥时候才能放我们出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.17,0:12:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说好不妨碍你们就可以继续旅行的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.14,0:12:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会尽快放你们出来的 不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.33,0:12:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地下的洞穴也是你们计划的一部分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被大家发现…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.85,0:12:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姆斯特朗少将会把人造人放回通道里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.22,0:12:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后封住洞穴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.44,0:12:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少将已经是我们的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.66,0:12:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下 不搜索失踪的先遣队吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.04,0:12:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴 亨舍尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.25,0:12:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们可能还活着 还在等待救援啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.21,0:12:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.41,0:12:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴服从命令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.88,0:12:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「服从力量」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.05,0:12:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难攻不落的布里格斯北壁也会屈服于权力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.32,0:12:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这样才是精明的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.31,0:13:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那就是传说中的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.12,0:13:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 史洛斯（Sloth）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.01,0:13:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡得好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.39,0:13:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想睡…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.49,0:13:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 你还有事情要做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.17,0:13:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莱德（Pride）不是跟你说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.80,0:13:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普莱德？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.73,0:13:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.41,0:13:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.65,0:13:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.28,0:13:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥 觉得麻烦来着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.00,0:13:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回忆也很麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为中央军工作的合成兽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.06,0:14:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让国家更强大而工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.17,0:14:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此 目前还是机密行动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.34,0:14:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快点把这个洞穴封住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.94,0:14:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里格斯的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.82,0:14:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是共享秘密的同志了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.28,0:14:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关键之处都改用古代伊修瓦尔语书写了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.27,0:14:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像故意不想让人看懂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.44,0:14:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能放弃了么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.28,0:14:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果斯卡在的话或许能读懂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊修瓦尔的武僧有可能懂得古代语言
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.75,0:14:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯卡先生不会出什么事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.88,0:14:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.29,0:14:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着黑白猫的小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我们上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.25,0:15:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯卡先生 尤基先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.56,0:15:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到研究书了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.78,0:15:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.93,0:15:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转移吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.37,0:15:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里被布里格斯士兵发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.67,0:15:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.25,0:15:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们被选中之人将获得接近神的肉体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.73,0:15:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并统治世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.48,0:15:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人叫史密斯来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.78,0:15:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先遣队的事情实在是没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.76,0:15:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了被选中的人 下级的人都要牺牲？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.11,0:15:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 弱肉强食
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱者成为国家的基石
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.26,0:15:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强者在上面尽享繁荣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.82,0:15:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道伊修瓦尔也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.60,0:15:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 那也是计划的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.44,0:15:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底弱民就是注定要被毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请务必交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.21,0:16:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.24,0:16:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.21,0:16:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你电话打得可真勤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.61,0:16:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷文中将在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.16,0:16:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有话要跟他说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.78,0:16:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重伤濒死的你当天就痊愈出现在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.98,0:16:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用了什么魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.00,0:16:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这跟你没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.77,0:16:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底 杀害长官而坐牢的你怎么会被释放
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.63,0:16:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说了 跟你没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.58,0:16:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个计划是什么时候开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.71,0:16:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说从建国就开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.75,0:16:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今在我这代即将完成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.81,0:16:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢你的协助 阿姆斯特朗少将
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.84,0:17:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会向上级申请为你准备一把交椅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.98,0:17:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.16,0:17:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史密斯的是左臂还是右臂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.16,0:17:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.13,0:17:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衰老还真是可怕呢 雷文中将
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.69,0:17:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想当年你曾是个忠心为国 年轻气盛的军人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.04,0:17:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然…你本可以成为被选中之人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.36,0:17:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这难得的椅子…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.79,0:17:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不用什么新的交椅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.06,0:17:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只须你挪开坐烂的屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.73,0:17:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把椅子让出来便是！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老不死的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.84,0:17:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长生不老…就在眼前啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.04,0:18:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就在此名副其实地成为国家的垫脚石吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.77,0:18:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷文中将
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.46,0:18:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要长生不老…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.78,0:18:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴卡尼亚 联系迈尔斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.72,0:18:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.97,0:18:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家继续
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.90,0:18:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水泥记得铺平
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.27,0:18:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.96,0:18:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可真有反抗精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.92,0:18:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是参与伊修瓦尔歼灭战的国家炼金术师？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.66,0:18:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样你才满意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.99,0:18:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道同族都是怎么死的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.61,0:18:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴 金布利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.56,0:18:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不我告诉你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.12,0:18:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我让你闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校打扰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.69,0:18:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姆斯特朗少将传话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.89,0:18:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「作战成功 不用再拖延时间了」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.81,0:19:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.62,0:19:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 终于不用跟他说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.93,0:19:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这戏演的太吃力了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.80,0:19:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金布利
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.88,0:19:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷文中将不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.87,0:19:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道他会去哪里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.80,0:19:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失踪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.49,0:19:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真糟糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.09,0:19:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里可没安全到外人可以随便溜达啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.62,0:19:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中将若有什么意外…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.22,0:19:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷文中将如有什么意外
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.22,0:19:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我便可依个人判断自由行动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.87,0:19:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总统已经批准了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.64,0:19:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能开车带我去山脚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.38,0:19:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迈尔斯少校
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.14,0:19:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.26,0:19:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我的行动就等于是总统的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.23,0:19:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下 阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.83,0:19:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在完全封闭洞穴之前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.47,0:20:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该先搜寻史密斯他们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.74,0:20:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就知道会发生这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.73,0:20:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以让钢仔开了个通道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀死了？把雷文中将？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.37,0:20:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我传完话了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.41,0:20:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我们什么时候才能出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊 你去问少将吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.19,0:20:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.85,0:20:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,着急也没用 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.46,0:20:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是趁机休息一下身体吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.48,0:20:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里都鸡飞狗跳了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.02,0:20:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么能冷静得下来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.49,0:20:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.53,0:20:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我申请来探望钢之炼金术师先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.56,0:20:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 难道我不受欢迎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.64,0:20:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我给两位带来一位客人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.08,0:20:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.12,0:21:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.62,0:21:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么 来给你换北方用的机械铠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.00,0:21:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说你怎么进了班房啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.23,0:21:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人叫你来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.02,0:21:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么这么说 我可担心你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.18,0:21:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好军队的人联系了我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.15,0:21:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,435)\fs23}（军队的人？）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.99,0:21:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩都冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.43,0:21:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总统阁下可是非常担心你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.03,0:23:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金布利？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.46,0:23:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.64,0:23:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在布里格斯山脚当护士的朋友告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.43,0:23:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他重伤住院
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.14,0:23:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却在雷文将军来探望之后马上痊愈出院了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.70,0:23:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷文和金布利
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.93,0:23:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的情报就这些
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.51,0:23:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了 以后有事还得靠你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.67,0:23:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有空再来我们店里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.09,0:23:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被甩了啊 小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.21,0:23:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要买束花追过去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.28,0:23:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这人比较容易死心 还是免了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.08,0:23:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有女人甩你 就会有女人要你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.00,0:23:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥莉薇·米拉·阿姆斯特朗少将有传话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.98,0:23:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗伊·玛斯坦上校
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.01,0:23:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你的花我全都包下了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------NEXT-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.48,0:24:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,束缚手脚的锁链以意外的形态出现
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.49,0:24:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年啊 挣脱粉碎锁链
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.25,0:24:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揭露暗中接近的敌人身份吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.28,0:24:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 钢之炼金术师
